sentences: Jake Allston (born 1986 in Glens Falls, NY) is an American sound designer.
Jake Allston (born 1986 in Glens Falls, NY) is an American sound designer.
Jake started his professional career designing sound effects for animated television shows at Advantage Audio in 2006.
section: == Career ==

sentences: Soon thereafter, he also edited audio for reality television at Max Post (Original Productions) in 2008 on various series including Deadliest Catch and Ice Road Truckers.
section: == Career ==

sentences: On August 30, 2009, Jake received an Emmy Award for his contributions as supervising sound editor on Nickelodeon's Tak and the Power of Juju.
section: == Career ==

sentences: "He began teaching Advanced Audio Post-Production at the Los Angeles Film School in 2015.
section: == Career ==

sentences: In 2017, Jake became senior cinematic sound designer for Sony PlayStation.
